title: Top 30 Country Oct 21, 2014 + recurrents
description:
Back in May 2014 in addition to the Top 30 Country Tracks I also included all of the songs which had fallen off of the charts since January 1 of this year.  By request, here are is the second batch of songs that have hit the charts since May 6 but have since dropped out (36 in total).  This week itÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s a healthy debut from Kenny Chesney and Brett Eldredge squeaks in at #30 with his latest single.  All songs are mp3 constant bit rate (CBR) stereo.  Happy Halloween and see you again in two weeks with another new Top 30 U.S. Country singles chart as ranked by Mediabase.
